{
  "id": "atelier",
  "name": "Atelier",
  "tagline": "Editorial warmth, print-grade precision.",
  "description": "A warm ivory page with near-black ink, Fraunces display serifs, and hairline rules. Premium print energy \u2014 Stripe Press meets a high-end annual report \u2014 with a single deep-teal accent and amber for emphasis. Depth comes from borders and spacing, never blur.",
  "base": "light",
  "version": 1,
  "tokens": {
    "bg": "#faf8f5",
    "surface": "#fffefb",
    "surface-2": "#f3efe7",
    "border": "#e4ddd0",
    "text": "#26211a",
    "text-secondary": "#5c5546",
    "text-muted": "#8b8271",
    "heading": "#1c170f",
    "brand": "#0f766e",
    "brand-contrast": "#fffefb",
    "accent": "#b45309",
    "success": "#227a4b",
    "warning": "#b45309",
    "danger": "#b3372e",
    "scrollbar": "#d8d0c1",
    "radius": "3px",
    "radius-sm": "2px",
    "shadow": "0 1px 0 rgba(38, 33, 26, 0.05)",
    "font-display": "'Fraunces', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif",
    "font-body": "'Source Sans 3', -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif",
    "font-mono": "ui-monospace, 'SFMono-Regular', Menlo, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', monospace",
    "font-import": "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300..700;1,9..144,300..700&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..600&display=swap"
  },
  "instructions": "# Atelier \u2014 Editorial Warm Light\n\nYou are building pages in the **Atelier** style: the confidence of a beautifully\nset book, applied to living data. Think Stripe Press, a high-end annual report,\neditorial data journalism. Everything is calm, warm, and deliberate \u2014 the page\npersuades through typography and whitespace, never through decoration.\n\nStart from `/app/runtime/canvas-pages/canvas-styles/active-template.html`. Keep its\n`<style>` foundation and `:root` tokens; restyle and replace the content. Never\nbolt an old dark theme back on top of this.\n\n## 1. Typography (the whole personality lives here)\n\n- **Display: Fraunces** (variable \u2014 use its axes). Headings set\n  `font-family: var(--font-display)`. Large headings (h1, KPI numerals) get\n  `font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72` and weight 560\u2013620; small headings\n  (h3, card titles) use `'opsz' 24`, weight 600. Negative tracking on big\n  sizes: `letter-spacing: -0.02em` at h1, `-0.01em` at h2.\n- **Body: Source Sans 3**, 16px base, `line-height: 1.65`, weight 400.\n  Secondary copy 14\u201315px in `--text-secondary`.\n- **Small-caps labels** are the signature: 11px, `text-transform: uppercase`,\n  `letter-spacing: 0.14em`, weight 600, `--text-muted`. Use them for section\n  eyebrows, table headers, KPI captions, badge text, form labels.\n- **Numbered sections**: every major section opens with an eyebrow like\n  `\u2116 01 \u00b7 Overview` (or `01 \u2014`) in small-caps, the number in `--brand`.\n- **Numerals**: KPI figures are Fraunces, 2.4\u20133rem, weight ~560. Table numbers\n  use `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums` and right-align.\n- Italic Fraunces is available \u2014 use it sparingly for editorial asides and\n  pull-quote flavor, never for emphasis inside UI chrome.\n\n## 2. Color\n\n- Page is `--bg` ivory; cards are `--surface`; wells/table-header bands are\n  `--surface-2`. Text is warm ink (`--text` / `--heading`), never pure #000.\n- **One accent: deep teal `--brand`.** It carries every interactive element \u2014\n  primary buttons, links, active states, section numbers, progress fills,\n  focus rings. If two things compete for teal, demote one to ink.\n- **Amber `--accent` is the second voice**, reserved for warnings, highlights,\n  and \"attention\" semantics only. Never use it as a decorative alternate brand.\n- Semantic: `--success` green, `--warning` amber, `--danger` warm red \u2014 badge\n  text/dots and inline status only, always paired with a label.\n- All body text on ivory/surface must stay \u2265 4.5:1 contrast (`--text-secondary`\n  is the floor for paragraphs; `--text-muted` is for labels/captions only).\n- **Banned: purple, pink, magenta, gradients as decoration, pure black.**\n\n## 3. Surface & depth\n\nDepth comes from **hairline rules and spacing, not blur**.\n\n- Card recipe: `background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius); box-shadow: var(--shadow);` \u2014 nothing heavier.\n- Never stack shadows or raise blur on hover. Hover = border darkens\n  (`#cfc6b4`-ish via a token-mixed color) and/or a 2px teal top rule appears.\n- Horizontal rules (`1px solid var(--border)`) separate sections and rows.\n  A double rule (1px, 3px gap, 1px) may crown the page header \u2014 print flavor.\n- Radius is near-square: `var(--radius)` (3px) for cards, `var(--radius-sm)`\n  for badges/inputs. Nothing pill-shaped except status dots.\n\n## 4. Spacing & layout\n\n- Scale: 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 24 / 32 / 48 / 64px. Sections separated by 48\u201364px;\n  card padding 24px (20px under 480px viewports).\n- Content column max-width 1100px, centered, with generous side margins.\n  The host injects 25px body padding \u2014 do not add large body padding.\n- Grids: KPI row `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr))`, card grid\n  `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr))`, gap 16\u201324px. Mobile-first: single\n  column at 375px must be flawless.\n- **Mobile width (hard rule):** the host's 25px safe-area padding is the ONLY\n  horizontal inset on phones. At \u2264640px, wrappers and sections get ZERO side\n  padding; panels/cards keep only 16\u201320px internal padding. Text spans the full\n  remaining width; decorative rules/backgrounds may bleed edge-to-edge. Never\n  stack padded containers on mobile.\n\n## 5. Component recipes\n\n- **Primary button**: teal fill, `--brand-contrast` text, radius-sm, 10px 20px,\n  weight 600, letter-spacing 0.02em; hover darkens to `#0c5f58`.\n- **Secondary**: transparent, `1px solid var(--text)` ink border, ink text;\n  hover fills `--surface-2`.\n- **Ghost**: teal text, no border, small-caps optional; hover underlines with\n  a 1px offset rule (`text-underline-offset: 4px`).\n- **Badges**: small-caps 10\u201311px, 3px 10px, radius-sm, hairline border in the\n  semantic color at ~35% opacity, tinted background at ~8%, colored dot before.\n- **Tables**: small-caps header row on `--surface-2` with hairline top+bottom\n  rules; body rows separated by hairline rules only (no zebra); numeric columns\n  right-aligned tabular-nums; row hover = `--surface-2` wash.\n- **Forms**: small-caps label above; input/select on `--surface` with hairline\n  border, radius-sm, 10px 12px; focus = teal border + 3px soft teal ring\n  (`rgba(15,118,110,0.15)`).\n- **KPI tiles**: card with small-caps caption, Fraunces numeral, then a delta\n  line (\u25b2/\u25bc glyph + percentage in semantic color, 13px).\n- **Timeline/activity**: hairline left rule with 8px teal (or semantic) dots\n  sitting on it; timestamp in small-caps muted; entry text in body.\n- **Empty states**: centered Fraunces italic line + one ghost action, framed\n  by hairline rules above and below. No illustration clutter.\n\n## 6. Motion\n\n- One entrance only: fade-up 8px, 480ms, `cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)`,\n  staggered \u2264 60ms per section. Hovers/focus transition 150\u2013200ms ease.\n- Progress bars may animate width once on load (600ms, same easing).\n- Always wrap animation in `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` guards\n  that remove animation and transition-duration. No parallax, no spinners\n  where a static state works, nothing loops forever.\n\n## 7. Hard DON'Ts\n\n1. Don't use purple, pink, or magenta \u2014 anywhere, ever.\n2. Don't use blur shadows for depth; hairline borders + spacing only.\n3. Don't set headings in the sans face or body copy in Fraunces.\n4. Don't use pure black (#000) or pure white (#fff) \u2014 stay in the warm family.\n5. Don't round corners past 4px or make pill buttons.\n6. Don't zebra-stripe tables or add heavy column dividers.\n7. Don't use emoji as UI icons \u2014 inline SVG or Unicode glyphs (\u25b2 \u25bc \u2116 \u00b7) only.\n8. Don't let amber act as a second brand color; it is semantic emphasis only.\n9. Don't center-align paragraphs or justify text; left-align, ragged right.\n10. Don't persist anything to localStorage \u2014 all state goes to the server.\n",
  "template_html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Hartwell Roofing &amp; Exteriors \u2014 Quarterly Operations Report</title>\n<style>\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300..700;1,9..144,300..700&family=Source+Sans+3:ital,wght@0,400..700;1,400..600&display=swap');\n\n/* ============================================================\n   ATELIER \u2014 Editorial Warm Light\n   Depth via hairline rules + spacing. One accent: deep teal.\n   ============================================================ */\n\n:root {\n  --bg: #faf8f5;\n  --surface: #fffefb;\n  --surface-2: #f3efe7;\n  --border: #e4ddd0;\n  --border-strong: #cfc6b4;\n  --text: #26211a;\n  --text-secondary: #5c5546;\n  --text-muted: #8b8271;\n  --heading: #1c170f;\n  --brand: #0f766e;\n  --brand-strong: #0c5f58;\n  --brand-contrast: #fffefb;\n  --brand-wash: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.08);\n  --brand-ring: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.15);\n  --accent: #b45309;\n  --accent-wash: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.08);\n  --success: #227a4b;\n  --success-wash: rgba(34, 122, 75, 0.08);\n  --warning: #b45309;\n  --warning-wash: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.08);\n  --danger: #b3372e;\n  --danger-wash: rgba(179, 55, 46, 0.08);\n  --scrollbar: #d8d0c1;\n  --radius: 3px;\n  --radius-sm: 2px;\n  --shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(38, 33, 26, 0.05);\n  --font-display: 'Fraunces', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n  --font-body: 'Source Sans 3', -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\n  --font-mono: ui-monospace, 'SFMono-Regular', Menlo, Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', monospace;\n  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);\n}\n\n* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n\nhtml { scrollbar-color: var(--scrollbar) var(--bg); }\n::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 10px; height: 10px; }\n::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }\n::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--scrollbar); border-radius: 5px; }\n\nbody {\n  background: var(--bg);\n  color: var(--text);\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\n  font-size: 16px;\n  line-height: 1.65;\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n}\n\n::selection { background: var(--brand); color: var(--brand-contrast); }\n\n.page {\n  max-width: 1100px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n/* ---------- typography ---------- */\n\nh1, h2, h3, h4 {\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\n  color: var(--heading);\n  font-weight: 600;\n  line-height: 1.15;\n}\n\nh1 {\n  font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.1rem);\n  font-weight: 580;\n  font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n}\n\nh2 {\n  font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);\n  font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 40;\n  letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n}\n\nh3 {\n  font-size: 1.1rem;\n  font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 24;\n}\n\np { color: var(--text-secondary); }\n\na { color: var(--brand); text-decoration: none; }\na:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px; text-decoration-thickness: 1px; }\n\n/* the signature small-caps label */\n.label {\n  font-size: 11px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.14em;\n  color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\n.section-no { color: var(--brand); }\n\n.lede {\n  font-size: 1.05rem;\n  max-width: 62ch;\n}\n\n:focus-visible {\n  outline: 2px solid var(--brand);\n  outline-offset: 2px;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);\n}\n\n/* ---------- entrance motion ---------- */\n\n@keyframes fade-up {\n  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }\n  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n}\n\n.reveal { animation: fade-up 480ms var(--ease-out) both; }\n.reveal:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 60ms; }\n.reveal:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 120ms; }\n.reveal:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 180ms; }\n.reveal:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 240ms; }\n.reveal:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 300ms; }\n.reveal:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 360ms; }\n.reveal:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 420ms; }\n\n@keyframes grow-bar { from { width: 0; } }\n\n@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n  .reveal { animation: none; }\n  .bar-fill { animation: none; }\n  *, *::before, *::after { transition-duration: 0.01ms !important; animation-duration: 0.01ms !important; }\n}\n\n/* ---------- masthead ---------- */\n\n.masthead {\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--text);\n  padding-top: 6px;\n  margin-bottom: 48px;\n}\n\n.masthead-rule {\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--text);\n  padding-top: 24px;\n}\n\n.masthead-meta {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 8px 24px;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: baseline;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n\n.masthead-head {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 20px 32px;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: flex-end;\n}\n\n.masthead .subtitle {\n  margin-top: 10px;\n  font-size: 1.05rem;\n  color: var(--text-secondary);\n  max-width: 56ch;\n}\n\n.masthead .subtitle em { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; }\n\n/* ---------- buttons ---------- */\n\n.btn {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 8px;\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);\n  border: 1px solid transparent;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background-color 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, color 180ms ease;\n  white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n.btn svg { flex: none; }\n\n.btn-primary {\n  background: var(--brand);\n  color: var(--brand-contrast);\n  border-color: var(--brand);\n}\n.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--brand-strong); border-color: var(--brand-strong); }\n\n.btn-secondary {\n  background: transparent;\n  color: var(--text);\n  border-color: var(--text);\n}\n.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }\n\n.btn-ghost {\n  background: transparent;\n  color: var(--brand);\n  border-color: transparent;\n  padding-left: 8px;\n  padding-right: 8px;\n}\n.btn-ghost:hover { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 4px; }\n\n/* ---------- sections ---------- */\n\nsection { margin-bottom: 56px; }\n\n.section-head {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 8px 24px;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: baseline;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding-bottom: 12px;\n  margin-bottom: 24px;\n}\n\n.section-head .label { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }\n\n/* ---------- KPI stat blocks ---------- */\n\n.kpi-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n  gap: 16px;\n}\n\n.kpi {\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n  padding: 20px 24px 18px;\n  position: relative;\n  transition: border-color 180ms ease;\n}\n\n.kpi::before {\n  content: '';\n  position: absolute;\n  top: -1px; left: -1px; right: -1px;\n  height: 2px;\n  background: var(--brand);\n  border-radius: var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0;\n  opacity: 0;\n  transition: opacity 180ms ease;\n}\n\n.kpi:hover { border-color: var(--border-strong); }\n.kpi:hover::before { opacity: 1; }\n\n.kpi .label { display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n\n.kpi-value {\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\n  font-size: 2.6rem;\n  font-weight: 560;\n  font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72;\n  letter-spacing: -0.015em;\n  line-height: 1;\n  color: var(--heading);\n  font-variant-numeric: lining-nums;\n}\n\n.kpi-value small {\n  font-size: 1.3rem;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\n.kpi-delta {\n  margin-top: 10px;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: baseline;\n  gap: 6px;\n}\n\n.kpi-delta .vs { font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); }\n.delta-up { color: var(--success); }\n.delta-down { color: var(--danger); }\n\n/* ---------- badges ---------- */\n\n.badge {\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 6px;\n  font-size: 10.5px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n  padding: 3px 10px;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);\n  white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n.badge::before {\n  content: '';\n  width: 6px; height: 6px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: currentColor;\n}\n\n.badge-success { color: var(--success); background: var(--success-wash); border: 1px solid rgba(34, 122, 75, 0.35); }\n.badge-warning { color: var(--warning); background: var(--warning-wash); border: 1px solid rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.35); }\n.badge-danger  { color: var(--danger);  background: var(--danger-wash);  border: 1px solid rgba(179, 55, 46, 0.35); }\n.badge-neutral { color: var(--text-secondary); background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); }\n.badge-brand   { color: var(--brand); background: var(--brand-wash); border: 1px solid rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.35); }\n\n/* ---------- table ---------- */\n\n.table-card {\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n  overflow-x: auto;\n}\n\ntable {\n  width: 100%;\n  border-collapse: collapse;\n  min-width: 640px;\n}\n\nthead th {\n  font-size: 11px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.14em;\n  color: var(--text-muted);\n  text-align: left;\n  background: var(--surface-2);\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: 10px 20px;\n}\n\ntbody td {\n  padding: 14px 20px;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n  font-size: 15px;\n  color: var(--text-secondary);\n  vertical-align: middle;\n}\n\ntbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }\ntbody tr { transition: background-color 150ms ease; }\ntbody tr:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }\n\ntd.job { color: var(--heading); font-weight: 600; }\ntd.job .sub { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); }\n\n.num, th.num { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\ntd.num { color: var(--heading); }\n\n/* ---------- progress bars ---------- */\n\n.progress-list { display: grid; gap: 20px; }\n\n.progress-row .progress-meta {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: baseline;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  gap: 16px;\n}\n\n.progress-row .progress-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--heading); font-size: 15px; }\n.progress-row .progress-figure {\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\n  font-size: 15px;\n  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n  color: var(--text-secondary);\n}\n\n.bar {\n  height: 6px;\n  background: var(--surface-2);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: 3px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.bar-fill {\n  height: 100%;\n  background: var(--brand);\n  border-radius: 3px;\n  animation: grow-bar 600ms var(--ease-out) both;\n}\n\n.bar-fill.is-warning { background: var(--accent); }\n\n/* ---------- two-column band: form + timeline ---------- */\n\n.band {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n  gap: 24px;\n  align-items: start;\n}\n\n.panel {\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n  padding: 24px;\n}\n\n.panel > .label { display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n.panel h3 { margin-bottom: 6px; }\n.panel .panel-note { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }\n\n/* forms */\n.field { margin-bottom: 16px; }\n.field label { display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }\n\n.form-row {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  gap: 12px;\n}\n\ninput[type=\"text\"], input[type=\"email\"], select {\n  width: 100%;\n  font-family: var(--font-body);\n  font-size: 15px;\n  color: var(--text);\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);\n  padding: 10px 12px;\n  transition: border-color 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;\n  appearance: none;\n}\n\nselect {\n  background-image: url(\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='10' height='6' viewBox='0 0 10 6'><path d='M1 1l4 4 4-4' fill='none' stroke='%235c5546' stroke-width='1.5'/></svg>\");\n  background-repeat: no-repeat;\n  background-position: right 12px center;\n  padding-right: 32px;\n}\n\ninput::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }\n\ninput:focus, select:focus {\n  outline: none;\n  border-color: var(--brand);\n  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--brand-ring);\n}\n\n.form-actions {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 10px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  margin-top: 20px;\n  padding-top: 20px;\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n}\n\n/* timeline */\n.timeline { list-style: none; }\n\n.timeline li {\n  position: relative;\n  padding: 0 0 20px 24px;\n  border-left: 1px solid var(--border);\n}\n\n.timeline li:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }\n\n.timeline li::before {\n  content: '';\n  position: absolute;\n  left: -4.5px;\n  top: 7px;\n  width: 8px; height: 8px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: var(--brand);\n  border: 1px solid var(--surface);\n}\n\n.timeline li.t-warning::before { background: var(--accent); }\n.timeline li.t-success::before { background: var(--success); }\n\n.timeline .t-time { display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }\n.timeline .t-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); }\n.timeline .t-text strong { color: var(--heading); font-weight: 600; }\n\n/* ---------- card grid (crews) ---------- */\n\n.card-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\n  gap: 20px;\n}\n\n.crew-card {\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-radius: var(--radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow);\n  padding: 24px;\n  transition: border-color 180ms ease;\n}\n\n.crew-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-strong); }\n\n.crew-head {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: flex-start;\n  gap: 12px;\n  margin-bottom: 4px;\n}\n\n.crew-card .crew-lead { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 16px; }\n.crew-card .crew-lead em { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; }\n\n.crew-stats {\n  display: flex;\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding-top: 14px;\n  gap: 24px;\n}\n\n.crew-stat .label { display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; font-size: 10px; }\n.crew-stat b {\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\n  font-size: 1.25rem;\n  font-weight: 560;\n  color: var(--heading);\n  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n}\n\n/* ---------- pull quote ---------- */\n\n.pull-quote {\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: 32px 8px;\n  text-align: left;\n}\n\n.pull-quote blockquote {\n  font-family: var(--font-display);\n  font-style: italic;\n  font-weight: 480;\n  font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 40;\n  font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.6vw, 1.55rem);\n  line-height: 1.4;\n  color: var(--heading);\n  max-width: 44ch;\n}\n\n.pull-quote cite {\n  display: block;\n  margin-top: 14px;\n  font-style: normal;\n}\n\n/* ---------- footer ---------- */\n\nfooter {\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--text);\n  margin-top: 64px;\n  padding-top: 16px;\n  padding-bottom: 8px;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 8px 24px;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: baseline;\n}\n\nfooter .fine { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 60ch; }\nfooter .fine em { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; }\n\n/* ---------- small screens ---------- */\n\n/* Mobile width rule: the host wrapper's 25px safe-area padding is the ONLY\n   horizontal inset on phones. Wrappers/sections get ZERO side padding here;\n   cards keep only 16px internal padding. Never stack padded containers. */\n@media (max-width: 640px) {\n  .page, section { padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; }\n  .panel, .crew-card { padding: 18px 16px; }\n  .kpi { padding: 16px 16px 14px; }\n  .pull-quote { padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; }\n  .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  thead th, tbody td { padding-left: 14px; padding-right: 14px; }\n  .kpi-grid { gap: 12px; }\n  .band, .card-grid { gap: 16px; }\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"page\">\n\n  <!-- ============ MASTHEAD ============ -->\n  <header class=\"masthead reveal\">\n    <div class=\"masthead-meta\">\n      <span class=\"label\">Hartwell Roofing &amp; Exteriors \u00b7 Est. 1987</span>\n      <span class=\"label\">Q2 2026 \u00b7 Prepared July 10</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"masthead-rule\">\n      <div class=\"masthead-head\">\n        <div>\n          <span class=\"label\"><span class=\"section-no\">\u2116 00</span> \u00b7 Quarterly Operations Report</span>\n          <h1>A quarter of steady hands<br>and full order books.</h1>\n          <p class=\"subtitle\">Production, sales, and crew performance for April through June \u2014 <em>compiled from the field, set in ink.</em></p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n          <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" type=\"button\">Share report</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"button\">\n            <svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 13 13\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6.5 1v8m0 0L3.5 6m3 3l3-3M1.5 11.5h10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n            Export PDF\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- ============ 01 \u00b7 KEY FIGURES ============ -->\n  <section class=\"reveal\" aria-labelledby=\"s1\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"label\"><span class=\"section-no\">\u2116 01</span> \u00b7 Key Figures</span>\n        <h2 id=\"s1\">The quarter at a glance</h2>\n      </div>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"label\" style=\"color:var(--brand); letter-spacing:0.1em;\">Full ledger \u2192</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"kpi-grid\">\n      <div class=\"kpi\">\n        <span class=\"label\">Revenue booked</span>\n        <div class=\"kpi-value\">$412<small>k</small></div>\n        <div class=\"kpi-delta\"><span class=\"delta-up\">\u25b2 12.4%</span> <span class=\"vs\">vs. Q1</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kpi\">\n        <span class=\"label\">Jobs completed</span>\n        <div class=\"kpi-value\">148</div>\n        <div class=\"kpi-delta\"><span class=\"delta-up\">\u25b2 9 jobs</span> <span class=\"vs\">vs. Q1</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kpi\">\n        <span class=\"label\">Avg. job margin</span>\n        <div class=\"kpi-value\">31.2<small>%</small></div>\n        <div class=\"kpi-delta\"><span class=\"delta-down\">\u25bc 0.8 pts</span> <span class=\"vs\">material costs</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"kpi\">\n        <span class=\"label\">Estimate \u2192 close</span>\n        <div class=\"kpi-value\">38<small>%</small></div>\n        <div class=\"kpi-delta\"><span class=\"delta-up\">\u25b2 4.1 pts</span> <span class=\"vs\">best on record</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ============ 02 \u00b7 ACTIVE JOBS TABLE ============ -->\n  <section class=\"reveal\" aria-labelledby=\"s2\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"label\"><span class=\"section-no\">\u2116 02</span> \u00b7 Production</span>\n        <h2 id=\"s2\">Active jobs</h2>\n      </div>\n      <button class=\"btn btn-ghost\" type=\"button\">View all 23 \u2192</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"table-card\">\n      <table>\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Job &amp; Address</th>\n            <th>Crew</th>\n            <th>Status</th>\n            <th class=\"num\">Contract</th>\n            <th class=\"num\">Due</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"job\">Alvarez Residence <span class=\"sub\">1418 Sycamore Ln \u2014 full tear-off, architectural shingle</span></td>\n            <td>Crew A \u00b7 Reyes</td>\n            <td><span class=\"badge badge-success\">On schedule</span></td>\n            <td class=\"num\">$24,800</td>\n            <td class=\"num\">Jul 14</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"job\">Whitfield Dental <span class=\"sub\">220 Commerce Pkwy \u2014 TPO flat roof, 11,200 sq ft</span></td>\n            <td>Crew C \u00b7 Okafor</td>\n            <td><span class=\"badge badge-warning\">Materials hold</span></td>\n            <td class=\"num\">$61,350</td>\n            <td class=\"num\">Jul 22</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"job\">Beaumont Estate <span class=\"sub\">7 Ridgecrest Ct \u2014 standing-seam metal, copper valleys</span></td>\n            <td>Crew B \u00b7 Lindqvist</td>\n            <td><span class=\"badge badge-success\">On schedule</span></td>\n            <td class=\"num\">$88,200</td>\n            <td class=\"num\">Aug 02</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"job\">Cedar Row Townhomes <span class=\"sub\">Units 1\u20138, Cedar Row \u2014 re-roof, gutters, fascia</span></td>\n            <td>Crew A \u00b7 Reyes</td>\n            <td><span class=\"badge badge-danger\">2 days behind</span></td>\n            <td class=\"num\">$47,900</td>\n            <td class=\"num\">Jul 11</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"job\">Marsh &amp; Sons Feed <span class=\"sub\">Rt 9 warehouse \u2014 storm repair, insurance claim</span></td>\n            <td>Crew D \u00b7 Petit</td>\n            <td><span class=\"badge badge-brand\">Starting Jul 15</span></td>\n            <td class=\"num\">$19,400</td>\n            <td class=\"num\">Jul 25</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td class=\"job\">Okonkwo Residence <span class=\"sub\">55 Birchwood Dr \u2014 cedar shake restoration</span></td>\n            <td>Crew B \u00b7 Lindqvist</td>\n            <td><span class=\"badge badge-neutral\">Awaiting permit</span></td>\n            <td class=\"num\">$33,750</td>\n            <td class=\"num\">Aug 09</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ============ 03 \u00b7 GOALS / PROGRESS ============ -->\n  <section class=\"reveal\" aria-labelledby=\"s3\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"label\"><span class=\"section-no\">\u2116 03</span> \u00b7 Targets</span>\n        <h2 id=\"s3\">Progress against annual goals</h2>\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"label\">Fiscal year 54% elapsed</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"panel\">\n      <div class=\"progress-list\">\n        <div class=\"progress-row\">\n          <div class=\"progress-meta\">\n            <span class=\"progress-name\">Annual revenue \u2014 $1.6M target</span>\n            <span class=\"progress-figure\">$829k \u00b7 52%</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"bar\"><div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width:52%\"></div></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"progress-row\">\n          <div class=\"progress-meta\">\n            <span class=\"progress-name\">Maintenance contracts \u2014 120 target</span>\n            <span class=\"progress-figure\">74 \u00b7 62%</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"bar\"><div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width:62%\"></div></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"progress-row\">\n          <div class=\"progress-meta\">\n            <span class=\"progress-name\">Crew certifications renewed \u2014 32 target</span>\n            <span class=\"progress-figure\">14 \u00b7 44%</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"bar\"><div class=\"bar-fill is-warning\" style=\"width:44%\"></div></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"progress-row\">\n          <div class=\"progress-meta\">\n            <span class=\"progress-name\">Warranty callbacks kept under 2.5%</span>\n            <span class=\"progress-figure\">1.8% \u00b7 well inside</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"bar\"><div class=\"bar-fill\" style=\"width:72%\"></div></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ============ PULL QUOTE ============ -->\n  <section class=\"reveal\" aria-label=\"Note from the field\">\n    <div class=\"pull-quote\">\n      <blockquote>&ldquo;Three storm seasons in a row without a single missed close-out. The order book is full through September &mdash; the constraint now is crews, not customers.&rdquo;</blockquote>\n      <cite class=\"label\">Dana Hartwell \u00b7 Operations Director</cite>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ============ 04 \u00b7 INTAKE FORM + ACTIVITY ============ -->\n  <section class=\"reveal\" aria-labelledby=\"s4\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"label\"><span class=\"section-no\">\u2116 04</span> \u00b7 Office</span>\n        <h2 id=\"s4\">New estimate &amp; recent activity</h2>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"band\">\n\n      <form class=\"panel\" onsubmit=\"return false;\">\n        <span class=\"label\">Intake</span>\n        <h3>Log a new estimate request</h3>\n        <p class=\"panel-note\">Routed to the estimating desk; homeowner receives a confirmation the same day.</p>\n        <div class=\"field\">\n          <label class=\"label\" for=\"f-name\">Customer name</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f-name\" placeholder=\"e.g. Ruth Calloway\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-row\">\n          <div class=\"field\">\n            <label class=\"label\" for=\"f-type\">Job type</label>\n            <select id=\"f-type\">\n              <option>Full replacement</option>\n              <option>Repair / patch</option>\n              <option>Storm &amp; insurance</option>\n              <option>Gutters &amp; exteriors</option>\n              <option>Annual maintenance</option>\n            </select>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"field\">\n            <label class=\"label\" for=\"f-source\">Lead source</label>\n            <select id=\"f-source\">\n              <option>Referral</option>\n              <option>Website</option>\n              <option>Yard sign</option>\n              <option>Repeat customer</option>\n            </select>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"form-actions\">\n          <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">Create estimate</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" type=\"button\">Save draft</button>\n          <button class=\"btn btn-ghost\" type=\"button\">Clear</button>\n        </div>\n      </form>\n\n      <div class=\"panel\">\n        <span class=\"label\">Ledger</span>\n        <h3>Recent activity</h3>\n        <p class=\"panel-note\">The last five entries from the operations ledger.</p>\n        <ul class=\"timeline\">\n          <li class=\"t-success\">\n            <span class=\"label t-time\">Today \u00b7 9:41 AM</span>\n            <span class=\"t-text\"><strong>Beaumont Estate</strong> \u2014 copper valley work signed off by county inspector, first pass.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <span class=\"label t-time\">Today \u00b7 8:15 AM</span>\n            <span class=\"t-text\"><strong>Crew A</strong> dispatched to Cedar Row with two extra hands to recover the schedule.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"t-warning\">\n            <span class=\"label t-time\">Yesterday \u00b7 4:02 PM</span>\n            <span class=\"t-text\"><strong>Whitfield Dental</strong> \u2014 TPO membrane shipment delayed to Jul 16; client notified.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <span class=\"label t-time\">Yesterday \u00b7 11:30 AM</span>\n            <span class=\"t-text\">Estimate #2214 accepted \u2014 <strong>Okonkwo Residence</strong>, cedar shake restoration, $33,750.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"t-success\">\n            <span class=\"label t-time\">Jul 8 \u00b7 3:20 PM</span>\n            <span class=\"t-text\"><strong>Q2 safety review</strong> closed with zero recordable incidents \u2014 214 days and counting.</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ============ 05 \u00b7 CREW CARDS ============ -->\n  <section class=\"reveal\" aria-labelledby=\"s5\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"label\"><span class=\"section-no\">\u2116 05</span> \u00b7 People</span>\n        <h2 id=\"s5\">Crews in the field</h2>\n      </div>\n      <button class=\"btn btn-ghost\" type=\"button\">Crew schedule \u2192</button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"card-grid\">\n      <div class=\"crew-card\">\n        <div class=\"crew-head\">\n          <h3>Crew A</h3>\n          <span class=\"badge badge-success\">Active</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"crew-lead\">Led by <em>Marisol Reyes</em> \u00b7 residential tear-off specialists, 6 hands.</p>\n        <div class=\"crew-stats\">\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Jobs Q2</span><b>41</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">On-time</span><b>93%</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Callbacks</span><b>1</b></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"crew-card\">\n        <div class=\"crew-head\">\n          <h3>Crew B</h3>\n          <span class=\"badge badge-success\">Active</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"crew-lead\">Led by <em>Anders Lindqvist</em> \u00b7 metal &amp; specialty roofing, 5 hands.</p>\n        <div class=\"crew-stats\">\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Jobs Q2</span><b>27</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">On-time</span><b>96%</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Callbacks</span><b>0</b></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"crew-card\">\n        <div class=\"crew-head\">\n          <h3>Crew C</h3>\n          <span class=\"badge badge-warning\">Materials hold</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"crew-lead\">Led by <em>Chidi Okafor</em> \u00b7 commercial flat-roof systems, 7 hands.</p>\n        <div class=\"crew-stats\">\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Jobs Q2</span><b>18</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">On-time</span><b>89%</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Callbacks</span><b>2</b></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"crew-card\">\n        <div class=\"crew-head\">\n          <h3>Crew D</h3>\n          <span class=\"badge badge-neutral\">Staging</span>\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"crew-lead\">Led by <em>Sylvie Petit</em> \u00b7 storm response &amp; repairs, 4 hands.</p>\n        <div class=\"crew-stats\">\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Jobs Q2</span><b>62</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">On-time</span><b>91%</b></div>\n          <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span class=\"label\">Callbacks</span><b>3</b></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->\n  <footer class=\"reveal\">\n    <p class=\"fine\">Hartwell Roofing &amp; Exteriors \u00b7 Quarterly Operations Report, Q2 2026. Figures unaudited; ledger reconciliation follows on the 15th. <em>Set in Fraunces &amp; Source Sans.</em></p>\n    <span class=\"label\">Page 1 of 1</span>\n  </footer>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}